EFW2_Year_End_Employer_Filing_Data_Reque.description: When set to 1, data for all workers will be included in the response.  When set to 0, data for workers who haven't opted in of having their data automatically sent to tax preparation vendors will not be included in the response.  This boolean value should be set to 1 when the data from this web service is being sent to the Social Security Administration.  It should be set to 0 when the data is being sent to tax preparation vendors.
